{"tid":1755740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下屆垃圾會建制派扳回一城","createTime":"2019-11-25T17:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T18:48:38.000Z","uid":222513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6951276ff4a3f98bd9dcd2eac0c7bc5b44a6b3","tid":1755740,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"政府正研究居內地港人投票安排<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1755442/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1755442/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌大家係咪唔記得咗聶德權條仆街偷步買樓</span> <br />\n等國際線真係等到蚊訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己香港自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行集會主題可多樣化 <span style=\"color: red;\">清廉香港 五大訴求 缺一不可</span> 要有多方面對訴求嘅理解 係下屆垃圾會之前至少要爭取中間選民支持(我都好撚憎佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但五大訴求未達到之前要靠制度內嘅勝利令運動持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n當年有 <span style=\"color: red;\">杜松</span> 今年要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">杜德</span></span><br />\n屌要班狗官知道為虎作倀下場一定係要仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 警示世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道有人拗緊集會遊行/勇武 但都係大家有諗法就拋出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"da3b8300916013d22ac6f93ff807e38b536fb300","tid":1755740,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:45:58.000Z","msg":"仲有鄭若嬅條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拉埋佢同聶德權一齊講又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef400ff79ce098228dbb44d01c1e13247d72793","tid":1755740,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:46:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下家長車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"},{"pid":"d31c9cd93d3f615ca541b5adbf3d44c3af5382a3","tid":1755740,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"知道大家對警暴怒不可遏 <br />\n但制度嘅崩壞下唔單止有濫暴嘅警察 仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">濫權嘅官員</span> ！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ea99b16b5586004c038112b80bff3ce30230c1","tid":1755740,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"對準<span style=\"color: red;\">制度</span> 劍指<span style=\"color: red;\">政權</span>"},{"pid":"e35271e3336c40d6cac22ccaf97a1f2a76fa06e3","tid":1755740,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:49:55.000Z","msg":"本身有功能組別又比例代表制又DQ都冇可能過到半數<br />\n呢個係制度問題，正因為垃圾會制度問題先迫到我地要出嚟打<br />\n所以對垃圾會唔好有咁多期望，同區議會單議席全直選好唔同㗎"},{"pid":"bf5c5f4e777cb62a15d657a37661bba2c9b9f784","tid":1755740,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"范國威好似已經向ICAC舉報咗聶德權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年ICAC 4個月就調查完梁錦松<br />\n<br />\n范國威舉已經舉報咗一個月<br />\n<br />\n仲有三個月<br />\n<br />\n知道而家戰線越越多 但唔好放過聶德權個仆街啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1976a36afa3b0bba4fc8d2dd02a66aa2d3489405","tid":1755740,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:51:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd2abd21d5db36c932c2059e014c234e2103106e","tid":1755740,"uid":222513,"like":0,"di